ings with Blue Cheese Dip","publishedAt":"2018-06-04T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"52 g","fat":"65.2 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"14.8 g","calories":"35556 kJ \/ 856 kcal"},"usefulItems":"large bowl, cling film, baking dish, paper towels, deep fat fryer, serving bowl, oven, refrigerator","hintsAndTricks":["Do not be tempted to skip the refrigeration step on this recipe - this makes the flour sticky and results in superbly crispy wings!","Any strong blue cheese should work in the dip, but Danish Blue or Gorgonzola Piccante are best."],"basicInfo":["easy","30m","1h 45m","5 portions"]}